		"description": "<p>You fill your allies with a thirst for glory and battle using your triumphant rallying cry. Expend and roll a Bardic Inspiration die to determine the number of rounds you can maintain concentration on this spell (minimum 1 round). Each target gains a bonus to attack and damage rolls equal to the number of rounds you have maintained concentration on this spell (maximum +4).</p><p>You cannot cast another spell through your spellcasting focus while concentrating on this spell.</p><p><strong><em>Cast at Higher Levels.</em></strong> You can maintain concentration on this spell for an additional round for each slot level above 3rd.</p><hr class=\"a5e-rule u-my-md\"><p><strong>Rare: Courageous Battlecry Ballad.</strong> Targets gain an expertise die on saving throws against fear.</p>",
